sufficient to meet the parent company's and its subsidiaries' cash requirements
from operations for the next twelve months and to complete the planned
integration-related and restructuring efforts.  As part of furthering its
business strategy, the  Company continues to explore the acquisition of or the
opportunity for strategic relationships with other businesses. One or more of
these opportunities could have an impact on the Company's liquidity through the
use of cash or the issuance of debt.


